ASOTemplate.OSScript:
Public Function Cmd_Change(index, Cmd, Timeout)
' Command is only processed if it is set to 1 or 0 If Cmd >= 2 Or Cmd < 0 Then Cmd_Change = False Exit Function End If
Dim WriteTags(3) WriteTags(0) = "RCmd" & index WriteTags(1) = "DA" & index WriteTags(2) = "TimingOut" & index WriteTags(3) = "CmdSense" & index
Dim WriteTagValues(3) 'RCmd = 0 'DA = 1 'TimingOut = 2 'CmdSense = 3
' Send to RTU If Cmd = 0 Then WriteTagValues(0) = False 'RCmd WriteTagValues(3) = 0 'CmdSense Else WriteTagValues(0) = True 'RCmd WriteTagValues(3) = 1 'CmdSense End If
'Start timeout for checkback 'StartCheckbackTimeout
' Start timeout for feedback If Timeout > 0 Then ' First cancel any existing timer in case the user pressed the reset button on the faceplate ' and then pressed the command button sCheckFeedbackFunction = "CheckFeedback" & index & "_Acyclic" oMe.SetAcyclic sCheckFeedbackFunction, 0 sCheckFeedbackFunction = "CheckFeedback" & index & "_Acyclic" 'because oMe.SetAcyclic changes the string oMe.SetAcyclic sCheckFeedbackFunction, Timeout WriteTagValues(2) = 1 'TimingOut Else WriteTagValues(2) = 0 'TimingOut End If
'Reset Cmd for next time 'WriteTagValues(0) = 2 'Cmd WriteTagValues(1) = 0 'DA
oMe.WriteMultiTags WriteTags, WriteTagValues Cmd_Change = True 'Reset Cmd for next time 'AdvanceToNextState False End Function
Public Function CheckDiscrepancy(Command, Feedback) If Command = 1 Then 'Command = close If Feedback = 2 Then '2 = switch closed CheckDiscrepancy = 0 Else CheckDiscrepancy = 1 End If Else 'Command = open If Feedback = 1 Then '1 = switch opened CheckDiscrepancy = 0 Else CheckDiscrepancy = 1 End If End If 'MsgBox "CheckDiscrepancy = " & CheckDiscrepancy End Function
Public Function SwitchPos(Command) If Command = 1 Then 'Command = close SwitchPos = 2 Else 'Command = open SwitchPos = 1 End If End Function
Function CheckFeedback_Acyclic(index) Dim ReadTags(3) Dim ReadTagValues(3) Dim ReadTagQualities(3)
ReadTags(0) = "Pos" & index ReadTags(1) = "CmdSense" & index ReadTags(2) = "TimingOut" & index ReadTags(3) = "DA" & index
oMe.ReadMultiTags ReadTags, ReadTagValues, ReadTagQualities
Dim WriteTags(1) Dim WriteTagValues(1) WriteTags(0) = "DA" & index WriteTags(1) = "TimingOut" & index
WriteTagValues(0) = ReadTagValues(3) 'DA write = DA read
If (ReadTagValues(2) > 0) Then 'TimingOut ' Check feed back and ' set discrepancy alarm or not WriteTagValues(0) = CheckDiscrepancy (ReadTagValues(1), ReadTagValues(0)) 'write oMe.DA0; read oMe.CmdSense0, oMe.Pos0
' Reset discrepancy alarm If WriteTagValues(0) = 1 Then ResetDAInSeconds 60, index End If
End If
' Reset cmd for next time WriteTagValues(1) = 0 'oMe.TimingOut0
oMe.WriteMultiTags WriteTags, WriteTagValues End Function
Function PosAlarm(index)
Dim WriteTags(0) Dim WriteTagValues(0)
WriteTags(0) = "Pos" & index & "_ThrowAlarmMessage"
'Set alarm flag WriteTagValues(0) = 1
'Write alarm flag oMe.WriteMultiTags WriteTags, WriteTagValues
End Function
Function Pos_Change(index) Dim ReadTags(2) Dim ReadTagValues(2) Dim ReadTagQualities(2)
ReadTags(0) = "Pos" & index ReadTags(1) = "CmdSense" & index ReadTags(2) = "TimingOut" & index
oMe.ReadMultiTags ReadTags, ReadTagValues, ReadTagQualities
Dim WriteTags(0) Dim WriteTagValues(0) WriteTags(0) = "TimingOut" & index
If (ReadTagValues(2) > 0) Then 'oMe.TimingOut0 If CheckDiscrepancy (ReadTagValues(1), ReadTagValues(0)) = 0 Then 'oMe.CmdSense0, oMe.Pos0 WriteTagValues(0) = 0 'oMe.TimingOut0 sCheckFeedbackFunction = "CheckFeedback" & index & "_Acyclic" oMe.SetAcyclic sCheckFeedbackFunction, 0 oMe.WriteMultiTags WriteTags, WriteTagValues End If End If End Function
Function Pos_CheckForAlarmState(index) Dim ReadTags(1) Dim ReadTagValues(1) Dim ReadTagQualities(1)
ReadTags(0) = "Pos" & index ReadTags(1) = "Pos" & index & "_EnableBadPosAlarm"
'Read value and quality of Tags in ReadTags array oMe.ReadMultiTags ReadTags, ReadTagValues, ReadTagQualities
Dim WriteTags(0) Dim WriteTagValues(0) WriteTags(0) = "Pos" & index & "_ThrowAlarmMessage"
'Reset alarm flag WriteTagValues(0) = 0
'Write modified Tags oMe.WriteMultiTags WriteTags, WriteTagValues
'Abort of waiting acyclic fundtions sPosAlarmTimer = "Pos" & index & "_Alarm_Acyclic" oMe.SetAcyclic sPosAlarmTimer, 0
'Check if alarming should be used If (ReadTagValues(1) > 0) Then
'Check if Pos state is not Open or Closed If (ReadTagValues(0) < 1) Or (ReadTagValues(0) > 2) Then
'Call acyclic function with user delay sPosAlarmTimer = "Pos" & index & "_Alarm_Acyclic" oMe.SetAcyclic sPosAlarmTimer, oMe.CB_BadPosAlarmDelay End If End If End Function
'---------------------------------------------------------- TRIGGER ---------------------------------------------------------- Function Cmd0_Change() If oMe.TrackingMode Then If oMe.Cmd0 < 2 Then Dim value
value = SwitchPos(oMe.Cmd0) oMe.Pos0_Write value, oMe.TriggerTimestamp
oMe.Cmd0 = 2 oMe.Q0_TrackingMode = 1 End If Else If Cmd_Change(0, oMe.Cmd0, oMe.Timeout) Then oMe.Cmd0 = 2 End If End If End Function

oMe.Cmd9 = 2 oMe.Q9_TrackingMode = 1 End If Else If Cmd_Change(9, oMe.Cmd9, oMe.Timeout) Then oMe.Cmd9 = 2 End If End If End Function
Function Pos9_Change() Pos_Change(9)
'Set value from external Pos variable to the internal variable 'and change its timestamp to system time (with ts = 0) oMe.Pos9_Internal_Write oMe.Pos9, 0 End Function
Function CheckFeedback9_Acyclic() CheckFeedback_Acyclic(9) End Function
Function CheckOpTm() If oMe.OpTmAlarmLimit > 0 Then If oMe.OpTm >= oMe.OpTmAlarmLimit Then oMe.OpTmAlarm = 1 Else oMe.OpTmAlarm = 0 End If Else oMe.OpTmAlarm = 0 End If If oMe.OpTmWarnLimit > 0 Then If oMe.OpTm >= oMe.OpTmWarnLimit Then oMe.OpTmWarning = 1 Else oMe.OpTmWarning = 0 End If Else oMe.OpTmWarning = 0 End If End Function
Function OpTm_Change() CheckOpTm End Function
Function OpTmWarningChange() CheckOpTm End Function
Function OpTmAlarmChange() CheckOpTm End Function
Function CheckSwCount() If oMe.SwCountAlarmLimit > 0 Then If oMe.SwCount >= oMe.SwCountAlarmLimit Then oMe.SwCountAlarm = 1 Else oMe.SwCountAlarm = 0 End If Else oMe.SwCountAlarm = 0 End If If oMe.SwCountWarnLimit > 0 Then If oMe.SwCount >= oMe.SwCountWarnLimit Then oMe.SwCountWarning = 1 Else oMe.SwCountWarning = 0 End If Else oMe.SwCountWarning = 0 End If End Function
Function SwCount_Change() CheckSwCount End Function
Function SwCountAlarmChange() CheckSwCount End Function

Function QCONNERR_Change() If oMe.QCONNERR = 0 Then oMe.NoticeConnect = 1 oMe.TrackingMode = 0 oMe.Q0_TrackingMode = 0 oMe.Q1_TrackingMode = 0 oMe.Q2_TrackingMode = 0 oMe.Q8_TrackingMode = 0 oMe.Q9_TrackingMode = 0 oMe.QU_TrackingMode = 0 End If End Function
Function TrackingMode_Change() Dim value Dim time Dim quality
If oMe.QCONNERR = 0 And oMe.TrackingMode = 0 And oMe.NoticePositions = 1 Then oMe.NoticePositions = 0
oMe.Pos0_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos0_Write value, time
oMe.Pos1_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos1_Write value, time
oMe.Pos2_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos2_Write value, time
oMe.Pos8_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos8_Write value, time
oMe.Pos9_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos9_Write value, time
oMe.PosQU_Memory_Read value, time, quality oMe.PosQU_Write value, time End If
If oMe.QCONNERR = 1 And oMe.TrackingMode = 1 Then oMe.NoticePositions = 1
oMe.Pos0_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos0_Memory_Write value, time
oMe.Pos1_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos1_Memory_Write value, time
oMe.Pos2_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos2_Memory_Write value, time
oMe.Pos8_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos8_Memory_Write value, time
oMe.Pos9_Read value, time, quality oMe.Pos9_Memory_Write value, time
oMe.PosQU_Read value, time, quality oMe.PosQU_Memory_Write value, time End If End Function
Public Sub ResetDAInSeconds(lSeconds, index)
Select Case index Case 0 oMe.SetAcyclic "ResetDA0_Acyclic", lSeconds Case 1 oMe.SetAcyclic "ResetDA1_Acyclic", lSeconds Case 2 oMe.SetAcyclic "ResetDA2_Acyclic", lSeconds Case 8 oMe.SetAcyclic "ResetDA8_Acyclic", lSeconds Case 9 oMe.SetAcyclic "ResetDA9_Acyclic", lSeconds End Select End Sub

Public Function ResetDA2_Acyclic() oMe.DA2 = 0 End Function

Public Function ResetDA9_Acyclic() oMe.DA9 = 0 End Function
Public Function CancelTimeout(sAcyclicTimeoutName) Dim TOValue Dim TO_Timestamp Dim TO_Quality
If (oMe.TimingOut > 0) Then If LenB(sAcyclicTimeoutName) > 0 Then oMe.SetAcyclic sAcyclicTimeoutName, 0 ' Cancel Event End If oMe.TimingOut_Read TOValue, TO_Timestamp, TO_Quality TO_Timestamp = TO_Timestamp + CDbl(0.000011574074074) oMe.TimingOut_Write 0, TO_Timestamp End If End Function
